# Documentation Rule

README should explain:

- What the service does

- Why it exists

- Tech stack

- API flow

- Example log payload

- Maven commands

- Docker/Podman commands

- Deployment notes

- MVP limitations

- Future plans

Avoid overselling features that are not implemented.

Do not claim persistent log storage.

Do not claim full user authentication until it exists.